<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Living_machines&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.livingmachines.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.livingmachines.com/" rel="nofollow">Living Machines, Inc. Website</a></li>
